com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.directory

Interface Service


  • public interface Service
    The RDM Service. Contains information about a particular service.
    See Also:
    Service.ServiceFlags, Service.ServiceInfo, Service.ServiceState, Service.ServiceGroup, Service.ServiceLoad, Service.ServiceData, Service.ServiceLinkInfo
